es a tale of ancient gods in modern New York in "Wildfire in Manhattan." Vengeance is the heart of Richard Adams''s "The Knife." Jeffery Deaver introduces a dedicated psychologist whose mission in life is to save people in "The Therapist." A chilling punishment befitting an unspeakable crime is at the dark heart of Neil Gaiman''s novelette "The Truth Is a Cave in the Black Mountains."As it transforms your vi', NULL, 2011, '1407473107', '9781407473109', 374, NULL, NULL, 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/6430935-L.jpg', '/works/OL15173350W', NULL, '2011', 'English', NULL, 1, 0, 'stories-jodi-picoult', 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 'import_only', '2026-03-16 06:14:26', '2026-03-25 00:23:59');
